        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Asking protection against an attack by Col. Smith.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><persName>And Henry Esqr</persName></p>

<p>I have this moment been Called on by <persName>Colo Smyth</persName> to give up a
three pounder in my possession and as I have been told that my
<placeName>House </placeName>is to be forced to take it from me I pray you to make use of
your Authority as a <persName>piece officer</persName> and I demand that protection the
Laws of my <placeName>Country </placeName>give me&#8212;</p>

<p>[M. Austin.]</p>
<p>[Endorsed:] Memorandum Copy letter to <persName>A. Henry</persName> <date when="1806-07-04">July 4, 06</date></p>

        </div1>
